WEBVTT

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:30.336
but I decided to play a game

00:02:30.360 --> 00:02:34.976
where I imagined
that I am taking a role in a film,

00:02:35.000 --> 00:02:38.096
and in the film I am a waitress,

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:40.496
and I need to act great.

00:02:40.520 --> 00:02:44.696
I used to dye my hair
and brows to gingerette,

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:47.256
I changed my hair to curly perm,

00:02:47.280 --> 00:02:48.616
I lost weight

00:02:48.640 --> 00:02:51.136
and made myself believe

00:02:51.160 --> 00:02:55.256
I am just a character acting in a film.

00:02:55.280 --> 00:02:56.536
That isn't forever,

00:02:56.560 --> 00:02:59.376
that is all just temporary.

00:02:59.400 --> 00:03:00.816
That helped me a lot.